The paper discusses energy-efficient management of data centers, which is a topic related to computer networks and distributed systems. Therefore, cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) and cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) are the most likely sub-categories. The paper also mentions the application of group-server queues in communication networks, manufacturing systems, transportation networks, financial networks, and healthcare systems, which suggests that the paper may also belong to cs.SY (Systems and Control) and cs.PF (Performance). Finally, the paper discusses mathematical modeling and simulation, which is related to cs.IT (Information Theory).
